1.1.0
https://github.com/CodyTolene/pip-boy-3000-holotapes/pull/65
- Various cursor highlight changes, cursor size and movement input increased from 1px to 2px
- Added shade indication flavortext to the footer
- Added autosave text and autosaving text with different colors in the header which shows every 45 seconds, then changes back to "autosave" text
- Every 45 seconds a .img and .json file are written to holo/sukechi/ and are called upong rebooting up the holotape to allow the user to continue drawing from where they left off from last

